{"pageProps":{"bookPath":"leetcode","postPath":"lc-triangle","post":{"title":"【LeetCode】120. 三角形最小路径和","body":"<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>题目<a href=\"hhttps://leetcode-cn.com/problems/triangle/\">120. 三角形最小路径和</a>。这是个经典 DP 题目。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>首先我们找一下三角形的对应关系。设输入数组为 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mtext>t</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\textrm t</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.61508em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord textrm\">t</span></span></span></span></span>。如下图所示，<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mtext>t</mtext><mo stretchy=\"false\">[</mo><mi>i</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">]</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">[</mo><mi>j</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">]</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\textrm t[i][j]</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord textrm\">t</span></span><span class=\"mopen\">[</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">i</span><span class=\"mclose\">]</span><span class=\"mopen\">[</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05724em;\">j</span><span class=\"mclose\">]</span></span></span></span>\n上面的两个数分别是 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mtext>t</mtext><mo stretchy=\"false\">[</mo><mi>i</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy=\"false\">]</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">[</mo><mi>j</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy=\"false\">]</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\textrm t[i-1][j-1]</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord textrm\">t</span></span><span class=\"mopen\">[</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">i</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mclose\">]</span><span class=\"mopen\">[</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05724em;\">j</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mclose\">]</span></span></span></span> 和 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mtext>t</mtext><mo stretchy=\"false\">[</mo><mi>i</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy=\"false\">]</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">[</mo><mi>j</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">]</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\textrm t[i-1][j]</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord textrm\">t</span></span><span class=\"mopen\">[</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">i</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mclose\">]</span><span class=\"mopen\">[</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05724em;\">j</span><span class=\"mclose\">]</span></span></span></span>。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre>t = [                   [\n         [2],             [2],\n        [3,4],   ===&gt;     [3,4],\n       [6,5,7],           [6,5,7],\n      [4,1,8,3]           [4,1,8,3]\n    ]                   ]</pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>作为一个 DP 题目，我们应该 DP 什么呢？最开始我想的是每一层的最小路径，发现行不通，从第 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>i</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">i</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.65952em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">i</span></span></span></span> 层的最小路径推出不第\n<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>i</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">i+1</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.74285em;vertical-align:-0.08333em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">i</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span></span></span></span> 层的最小路径，反例还很好举。既然这样不行，就想着干脆求出第 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>i</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">i</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.65952em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">i</span></span></span></span> 层每个位置的最小路径好了，这样一来，\n我们就可以从第 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>i</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">i</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.65952em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">i</span></span></span></span> 层每个位置的最小路径，推出<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>i</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">i+1</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.74285em;vertical-align:-0.08333em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">i</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span></span></span></span> 层每个位置的最小路径，最终从最后一层每个位置的最小路径中\n选择最小的那个，就是答案了。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>记第 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>i</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">i</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.65952em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">i</span></span></span></span> 层 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>j</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">j</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.85396em;vertical-align:-0.19444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05724em;\">j</span></span></span></span> 号位置的最小路径为 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mtext>dp</mtext><mo stretchy=\"false\">[</mo><mi>i</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">]</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">[</mo><mi>j</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">]</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\textrm{dp}[i][j]</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord textrm\">dp</span></span><span class=\"mopen\">[</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">i</span><span class=\"mclose\">]</span><span class=\"mopen\">[</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05724em;\">j</span><span class=\"mclose\">]</span></span></span></span>。\n显然第 0 层的最小路径就是 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mtext>dp</mtext><mo stretchy=\"false\">[</mo><mn>0</mn><mo stretchy=\"false\">]</mo><mo>=</mo><mtext>t</mtext><mo stretchy=\"false\">[</mo><mn>0</mn><mo stretchy=\"false\">]</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\textrm{dp}[0] = \\textrm t[0]</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord textrm\">dp</span></span><span class=\"mopen\">[</span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mclose\">]</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord textrm\">t</span></span><span class=\"mopen\">[</span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mclose\">]</span></span></span></span>。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>如果已知第 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mtext>dp</mtext><mo stretchy=\"false\">[</mo><mi>i</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy=\"false\">]</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\textrm{dp}[i-1]</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord textrm\">dp</span></span><span class=\"mopen\">[</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">i</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mclose\">]</span></span></span></span>，那么第 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mtext>dp</mtext><mo stretchy=\"false\">[</mo><mi>i</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">]</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\textrm{dp}[i]</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord textrm\">dp</span></span><span class=\"mopen\">[</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">i</span><span class=\"mclose\">]</span></span></span></span> 要分三种情况计算：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"olist arabic\">\n<ol class=\"arabic\">\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mtext>t</mtext><mo stretchy=\"false\">[</mo><mi>i</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">]</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">[</mo><mn>0</mn><mo stretchy=\"false\">]</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\textrm t[i][0]</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord textrm\">t</span></span><span class=\"mopen\">[</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">i</span><span class=\"mclose\">]</span><span class=\"mopen\">[</span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mclose\">]</span></span></span></span> 位于左边，它上面只有一个数 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mtext>t</mtext><mo stretchy=\"false\">[</mo><mi>i</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy=\"false\">]</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">[</mo><mn>0</mn><mo stretchy=\"false\">]</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\textrm t[i-1][0]</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord textrm\">t</span></span><span class=\"mopen\">[</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">i</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mclose\">]</span><span class=\"mopen\">[</span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mclose\">]</span></span></span></span>。所以\n<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mtext>dp</mtext><mo stretchy=\"false\">[</mo><mi>i</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">]</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">[</mo><mn>0</mn><mo stretchy=\"false\">]</mo><mo>=</mo><mtext>dp</mtext><mo stretchy=\"false\">[</mo><mi>i</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy=\"false\">]</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">[</mo><mn>0</mn><mo stretchy=\"false\">]</mo><mo>+</mo><mtext>t</mtext><mo stretchy=\"false\">[</mo><mi>i</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">]</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">[</mo><mn>0</mn><mo stretchy=\"false\">]</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\textrm{dp}[i][0] = \\textrm{dp}[i-1][0] + \\textrm{t}[i][0]</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord textrm\">dp</span></span><span class=\"mopen\">[</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">i</span><span class=\"mclose\">]</span><span class=\"mopen\">[</span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mclose\">]</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord textrm\">dp</span></span><span class=\"mopen\">[</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">i</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mclose\">]</span><span class=\"mopen\">[</span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mclose\">]</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord textrm\">t</span></span><span class=\"mopen\">[</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">i</span><span class=\"mclose\">]</span><span class=\"mopen\">[</span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mclose\">]</span></span></span></span></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mtext>t</mtext><mo stretchy=\"false\">[</mo><mi>i</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">]</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">[</mo><mi>i</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">]</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\textrm t[i][i]</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord textrm\">t</span></span><span class=\"mopen\">[</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">i</span><span class=\"mclose\">]</span><span class=\"mopen\">[</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">i</span><span class=\"mclose\">]</span></span></span></span> 位于右边，它上面只有一个数 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mtext>t</mtext><mo stretchy=\"false\">[</mo><mi>i</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy=\"false\">]</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">[</mo><mi>i</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy=\"false\">]</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\textrm t[i-1][i-1]</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord textrm\">t</span></span><span class=\"mopen\">[</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">i</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mclose\">]</span><span class=\"mopen\">[</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">i</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mclose\">]</span></span></span></span>。所以\n<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mtext>dp</mtext><mo stretchy=\"false\">[</mo><mi>i</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">]</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">[</mo><mi>i</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">]</mo><mo>=</mo><mtext>dp</mtext><mo stretchy=\"false\">[</mo><mi>i</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy=\"false\">]</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">[</mo><mi>i</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy=\"false\">]</mo><mo>+</mo><mtext>t</mtext><mo stretchy=\"false\">[</mo><mi>i</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">]</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">[</mo><mi>i</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">]</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\textrm{dp}[i][i] = \\textrm{dp}[i-1][i-1] + \\textrm{t}[i][i]</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord textrm\">dp</span></span><span class=\"mopen\">[</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">i</span><span class=\"mclose\">]</span><span class=\"mopen\">[</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">i</span><span class=\"mclose\">]</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord textrm\">dp</span></span><span class=\"mopen\">[</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">i</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mclose\">]</span><span class=\"mopen\">[</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">i</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mclose\">]</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord textrm\">t</span></span><span class=\"mopen\">[</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">i</span><span class=\"mclose\">]</span><span class=\"mopen\">[</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">i</span><span class=\"mclose\">]</span></span></span></span></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mtext>dp</mtext><mo stretchy=\"false\">[</mo><mi>i</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">]</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">[</mo><mi>j</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">]</mo><mo>=</mo><mi>min</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mtext>dp</mtext><mo stretchy=\"false\">[</mo><mi>i</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy=\"false\">]</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">[</mo><mi>j</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy=\"false\">]</mo><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mtext>dp</mtext><mo stretchy=\"false\">[</mo><mi>i</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy=\"false\">]</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">[</mo><mi>j</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">]</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo>+</mo><mtext>t</mtext><mo stretchy=\"false\">[</mo><mi>i</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">]</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">[</mo><mi>j</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">]</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\textrm{dp}[i][j] = \\min(\\textrm{dp}[i-1][j-1], \\textrm{dp}[i-1][j]) +  \\textrm{t}[i][j]</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord textrm\">dp</span></span><span class=\"mopen\">[</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">i</span><span class=\"mclose\">]</span><span class=\"mopen\">[</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05724em;\">j</span><span class=\"mclose\">]</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mop\">min</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord textrm\">dp</span></span><span class=\"mopen\">[</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">i</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mclose\">]</span><span class=\"mopen\">[</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05724em;\">j</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mclose\">]</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord textrm\">dp</span></span><span class=\"mopen\">[</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">i</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mclose\">]</span><span class=\"mopen\">[</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05724em;\">j</span><span class=\"mclose\">]</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord textrm\">t</span></span><span class=\"mopen\">[</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">i</span><span class=\"mclose\">]</span><span class=\"mopen\">[</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05724em;\">j</span><span class=\"mclose\">]</span></span></span></span></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>这样的话，代码就呼之欲出了：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-ts\" data-lang=\"ts\"><span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">minimumTotal</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\">triangle: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">number</span>[][]</span>): <span class=\"hljs-title\">number</span> </span>{\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> dp: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">number</span>[][] = []\n    dp[<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>] = triangle[<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>]\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; i &lt; triangle.length; i++) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> dpi: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">number</span>[] = []; <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// dp[i]，我们要求它</span>\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> dpp = dp[i - <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>];    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// dp previous; dp[i-1]</span>\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> t = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>; t &lt;= i; t++) {\n            <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (t == <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>) {\n                dpi[t] = dpp[<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>] + triangle[i][t];\n            } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (t == i) {\n                dpi[t] = dpp[t - <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>] + triangle[i][t];\n            } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n                dpi[t] = <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">Math</span>.min(dpp[t - <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>], dpp[t]) + triangle[i][t];\n            }\n        }\n        dp[i] = dpi;\n    }\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">Math</span>.min(...dp[triangle.length - <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>])\n};</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>我们注意到代码中，在求 <code>dpi</code>（<code>dp[i]</code>） 的时候，只使用了 <code>dpp</code>（<code>dp[i-1]</code>），但是 <code>dp[i-更多]</code>\n没有被使用却被存了下来，浪费了空间。为了计算 <code>dp[i]</code>，我们只要保存 <code>dp[i-1]</code> 就好了，这样就可以把多使用的空间省下来了，\n这是一个空间复杂度从 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>O</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><msup><mi>n</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">O(n^2)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1.064108em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">O</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8141079999999999em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span> 到 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>O</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>n</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">O(n)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">O</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span> 的优化。因为原理都说清楚了，代码就不写了。</p>\n</div>","createTime":1609344000000,"authorName":"weily","type":"adoc"},"book":{"title":"LeetCode","toc":[{"title":"53. 最大子数组","path":"lc-maximum-subarray"},{"title":"62. 不同路径","path":"lc-unique-paths"},{"title":"63. 不同路径 II","path":"lc-unique-paths-ii"},{"title":"64. 最小路径和","path":"lc-minimum-path-sum"},{"title":"70. 爬楼梯","path":"lc-climbing-stairs"},{"title":"95. 不同的二叉搜索树 II","path":"lc-unique-binary-search-trees-ii"},{"title":"96. 不同的二叉搜索树","path":"lc-unique-binary-search-trees"},{"title":"120. 三角形最小路径和","path":"lc-triangle"},{"title":"121. 买卖股票","path":"lc-buy-stock"},{"title":"132. 分割回文串 II","path":"lc-palindrome-partitioning-ii"},{"title":"152. 乘积最大子数组","path":"lc-maximum-product-subarray"},{"title":"198. 打家劫舍","path":"lc-house-robber"},{"title":"256. 粉刷房子","path":"lc-paint-house"},{"title":"276. 栅栏涂色","path":"lc-paint-fence"},{"title":"303. 区域和检索 - 数组不可变","path":"lc-range-sum-query-immutable"},{"title":"746. 使用最小花费爬楼梯","path":"lc-min-cost-climbing-stairs"},{"title":"146. LRU 缓存机制","path":"lc-lru-cache"},{"title":"数完全二叉树节点","path":"lc-count-complete-tree-nodes"}],"path":"leetcode"}},"__N_SSG":true}